Text: Amai Liu is not the same person as Kitty. Amai's known aliases are Amai Liu, Amai Lui, Miss Amai, Tiny Tabby. Kitty, Miss Kitty and Little Kitty are not the same person as Amai. Both are tiny and asian though. Kitty is 25 and Amai is 20
